-- ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź
function Nexus:LoadingScreen(opts)
    opts = opts or {}
    local title = opts.Title or "NexusUI"
    local sub   = opts.Subtitle or "Loading..."
    local tasks = opts.Tasks or {}
    local T = (type(opts.Theme)=="table") and opts.Theme
              or Nexus.Themes[opts.Theme] or Nexus.Themes.BlackModern

    local sg = mkGui(99999)
    local bg = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(1,0,1,0), BackgroundColor3=T.bg,
        BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=1, Parent=sg})

    -- Subtle grid overlay
    N("ImageLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(0,600,0,600), Position=UDim2.new(.5,-300,.5,-300),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Image="rbxassetid://6014261993",
        ImageColor3=T.accent, ImageTransparency=.93, ZIndex=2, Parent=bg})

    local vp = getVP()
    local CW = math.min(400, vp.X-60)
    local CH = 232 + #tasks*26
    local card = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,CW,0,CH), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(.5,.5),
        Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.54,0), BackgroundColor3=T.section,
        BackgroundTransparency=1, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=3, Parent=bg})
    N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,10), Parent=card})          -- sharper 10px
    N("UIStroke",{Color=T.border, Thickness=1, Transparency=.2, Parent=card})

    -- Top accent stripe (2px)
    local topStripe = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,0,0,2),
        BackgroundColor3=T.accent, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,2), Parent=topStripe})

    -- Shimmer bar that slides across topStripe
    local shimmer = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,80,1,0), Position=UDim2.new(-0.3,0,0,0),
        BackgroundColor3=T.accentH, BackgroundTransparency=.4,
        BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=topStripe})
    N("UIGradient",{Transparency=NumberSequence.new({
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0,1),
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0.4,0.3),
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0.6,0.3),
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(1,1),
    }), Rotation=0, Parent=shimmer})

    tw(card,.45,{BackgroundTransparency=0, Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.5,0)})

    local y = 26
    N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,28), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=title, TextColor3=T.text, TextSize=22,
        Font=Enum.Font.GothamBold, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+34
    local subLbl = N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,16), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=sub, TextColor3=T.sub, TextSize=12,
        Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+24

    local checks = {}
    for i,tk in ipairs(tasks) do
        local row = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,22), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
            BackgroundTransparency=1, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
        local dot = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,6,0,6), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(0,.5),
            Position=UDim2.new(0,0,.5,0), BackgroundColor3=T.muted, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=row})
        N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=dot})
        local tl = N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-14,1,0), Position=UDim2.new(0,14,0,0),
            BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=tk.Name or ("Task "..i), TextColor3=T.muted,
            TextSize=12, Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, TextXAlignment=Enum.TextXAlignment.Left, ZIndex=5, Parent=row})
